nodes.text: Doctor Aphra 6 is the sixth issue of the canon comic book series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra. It was written by Alyssa Wong, illustrated by Ray-Anthony Height and Robert Gill, and published by Marvel Comics on November 25, 2020. It features the story "The Engine Job Part 1: Headhunted," in which the powerful Lady Domina Tagge puts a bounty on Chelli Aphra.

Someone sinister has put a price on DOCTOR APHRA's head… and it's none other than DOMINA TAGGE! Now Aphra's running for her life, trying to shake every bounty hunter on her tail. But one of those is SANA STARROS… and for Sana, it's personal! Aphra can't out-think Domina or outrun Sana…what choice does she have left?!
